{"tid":1643310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【天減賣國魚】韓國瑜升旗典禮大肆批評蔡英文，背後的國旗牆突然倒下","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:34:24.000Z","uid":38255,"like":962,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"f631edc388568d2803adf92a7d52ad4f782037bd","tid":1643310,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"今天雙十國慶，國民黨總統參選人、高雄市長韓國瑜一早參加市府自辦升旗典禮，這也是韓國瑜上任以來首次、高雄12年來首度舉辦國慶升旗活動，上午7點半，高市府宣布會場湧入兩萬人，現場旗海飄揚，韓國瑜致詞時，重砲抨擊民進黨讓台灣成了「東廠仍舊在、肥貓處處生」的高傲政府，呼籲台灣人與他共同打造「台灣安全，人民有錢」新政府，並喊出新台灣奇蹟。不過，韓慷慨激昂談話時，渾然不知他身後巨形國旗拼圖牆整面崩落，幸好一旁工作人員連忙用手頂住，才未擊中韓。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜本人於上午7:42抵達現場，並且在巨幅國旗拼圖上，拼上第100塊的拼圖圖案，先前有99位民眾已拼99塊。他在致詞過程中，這面<span style=\"color: red;\">大幅國旗拼圖牆突然掉落，一旁工作人員立即上前將國旗拼圖扶正，掛回去鋁架上，險些打到韓國瑜本人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtqJyrd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtqJyrd.jpg&h=b122c548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天神：X！差少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a80ff5847427f4659cb6bdb0133812af19a5d89","tid":1643310,"uid":20241,"like":382,"dislike":0,"score":382,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"蔣公顯靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3b1728de55fbe00c3acf145fff2a113ce39530","tid":1643310,"uid":228868,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"差少少咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" clas